신규 수록 논문 13편:
- ADA (MICCAI 2025): Learnable Bezier Remap per-sample adaptive aug [직접 경쟁 ★★★]
- MBFCV (MICCAI 2025): Multi-Branch vessel thickness discrimination [직접 경쟁 ★★★]
- GLCP (MICCAI 2025): Global-to-Local Connectivity Preservation
- CF_SEG (MICCAI 2025): Counterfactuals Meet Segmentation
- SPATIAL_TOPO (ICCV 2025 Workshop): Spatial-Aware Persistent Feature Matching
- GFSA (Pattern Recognition 2025): Generative Feature Style Augmentation
- FDGP (ICASSP 2025): Frequency Federated DG for Polyp
- CRISP (arXiv 2026): Rank-Guided Iterative Squeezing for Robust Seg
- FMS2 (arXiv 2026): Flow Matching for Thin Structure Seg & Synthesis
- SPOCKMIP (arXiv 2024): TOF-MRA vessel seg with MIP loss
- FPGM (arXiv 2025): Frequency Prior Guided Matching
- BOUNDLESS (arXiv 2024): Adaptive Feature Blending + DCAR
- DRIPS (medRxiv 2025): Domain Randomisation for PVS Seg

핵심 발견: ADA가 Bezier adaptive aug 아이디어를 공유하지만
image-level global conditioning vs structure-level local conditioning으로
granularity가 완전히 다름. thin vessel protection 개념 없음.

누적 총 논문: 44 → 57편
